+Causes
+.B gnome\-ssh\-askpass
+to grab the mouse pointer using
+.IR gdk_pointer_grab ()
+before asking for a passphrase.
+.PP
+Regardless of whether either of these environment variables is set,
+.B gnome\-ssh\-askpass
